{
  "texts": [
    "The prediction accuracy of sgRNA activity under label coding, one-hot coding and two-coding is higher than that of other length sequences under the same coding (Figure 1).",
    "(A) The position relationship between target flanker sequence and sgRNA sequence.",
    "The yellow fragment is the sgRNA sequence, the pink fragment is the target sequence, and the target sequence extending from left to right is the flanker sequence.",
    "(B) Schematic diagram of label coding mode.",
    "The bases A, T, C and G in the sequence are coded respectively to correspond to four different colors."
  ]
}